## Naming Conventions

- Route files: `stage01.routes.js`, `stage02.routes.js`
- Agent files: `agent01_missionFraming.js`, `agent04_sowExtraction.js`
- Middleware files: `hardStopGate.js`, `tierGate.js`, `authMiddleware.js`
- Component files: PascalCase — `StakeholderMap.jsx`, `MissionFramingForm.jsx`
- Supabase queries: always `async/await`, always handle errors explicitly

