## What to Do When You're Unsure

If a code decision touches any of the following, stop and ask before generating:
- Gate logic (Hard Stop, tier enforcement, reconciliation)
- Community voice data (how it's stored, retrieved, or displayed)
- Claude API call structure or system prompts
- RLS policies
- Tier access control

Do not guess on these. Ask.
